# Digital Piano using Arduino

## Objective
To create a simple digital piano using push buttons and a piezo buzzer.

## Components
- Arduino UNO
- 4 Push Buttons
- Piezo Buzzer
- Breadboard
- Jumper Wires

## Connections
- Buttons connected to D2-D5
- Buzzer connected to D8

## Working
Each button corresponds to a musical note. When pressed, the buzzer generates the selected frequency using the `tone()` function.

## Concepts Used
- Digital Inputs
- Arrays
- Functions
- Buzzer Control
- Serial Communication
